headline: Home Builders Stocks Q2 In Review: NVR (NYSE:NVR) Vs Peers
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at home builders stocks, starting with NVR (NYSE:NVR).
